      "content": "thanks for this. it's a good start but it feels a little too \"template-y\" for someone who spent 4 hours interviewing with our team. can you make it sound a bit more personalized? maybe add a sentence or two that acknowledges how much we actually enjoyed getting to know them, so it doesn't feel like a cold automated response?",
