      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior DevOps Position – Decision Update\n\nDear [Candidate Name],\n\nI really enjoyed the discussion we had regarding the technical aspects of our vision and the innovative projects we've been working on, especially how you shared insights on orchestrating containerized applications. Moreover, I appreciated your enthusiasm during the conversation about our culture and agile project management methods.\n\nAfter careful consideration and comparison with all candidates, we've decided to proceed with another team member who has more extensive experience specifically in Kubernetes orchestration. I know this wasn't the news you were hoping for, so I want to personally thank you for your interest in joining our team and for the time and insight you generously shared.\n\nWe truly value your candid experience with our company, and we encourage you to apply for any future roles that suit your qualifications. We wish you the very best in your career endeavors going forward.\n\nWarm regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Company]",
